race.comment: BRAVE DRAGON (5) raced in much stronger company through his last campaign and will find this easier coming back to maiden company. The inside draw should see him close to the speed  and he'll be fitter for a recent trial coming in. His formlines read very well for a race of this calibre and a bold showing is expected. REGGIO CALABRIA (1) gets the blinkers on first time today following a 1.8L defeat last time out when closing late from midfield. Drawn better this time around with Hearn replacing the apprentice hoop and he can sit closer out in trip. At his peak now and can make his presence felt. VALID POINT (2) led fresh but felt the pinch late when ending up 1.1L off the winner here. The wide draw is a query, but he'll be fitter now and has the speed to offset the gate. Can give a bold sight. NAILED'EM (6) trialled very impressively here recently and is not to be discounted. CAPRICIOUS RULER (8) can improve in this suitable event.
